WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: EtDyyadvAq0

NOTE Language: en

00:10:03.230 --> 00:10:08.130
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:10:16.040 --> 00:10:18.110
Yesterday at the very outset,

00:10:18.240 --> 00:10:22.080
I told you that truth is what it is.

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:25.190
If we have not found the truth

00:10:26.120 --> 00:10:29.120
we should be humble and honest about it,

00:10:30.010 --> 00:10:34.010
because truth is for our benevolence,

00:10:35.040 --> 00:10:38.170
for the benevolence of our city,

00:10:39.210 --> 00:10:41.120
of our society,

00:10:42.010 --> 00:10:45.180
of our country and of the whole universe.

00:10:46.150 --> 00:10:50.070
This is a very special time you are all born,

00:10:50.210 --> 00:10:56.210
where people have to get their Self-realization.

00:10:58.030 --> 00:11:01.170
This is the Resurrection Time as described in the Bible,

00:11:02.110 --> 00:11:06.220
it's the time of Kiyama as described by Mohammed Sahib.

00:11:08.110 --> 00:11:11.120
This is a very special time when Nala,

00:11:11.200 --> 00:11:14.000
as you know, Nala damayanthi akhyan -

00:11:14.150 --> 00:11:18.170
Nala was faced with Kali.

00:11:19.090 --> 00:11:22.070
He got very angry with Kali and said that

00:11:22.130 --> 00:11:25.120
"You have destroyed my family, you have destroyed my peace,

00:11:25.210 --> 00:11:28.120
and you put people into bhram,

00:11:28.240 --> 00:11:30.070
into illusions,

00:11:30.190 --> 00:11:33.160
so I'd better kill you."

00:11:37.190 --> 00:11:40.240
He challenged

00:11:41.190 --> 00:11:44.220
Kali that "You should be finished forever."

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:49.140
Then Kali said, "All right, let me tell you my mahatmyam.

00:11:50.010 --> 00:11:52.150
Let me tell you why I should be there.

00:11:53.040 --> 00:12:01.040
If I convince you then you can stop killing me,

00:12:01.130 --> 00:12:03.240
but if I do not, you can kill me."

00:12:05.150 --> 00:12:11.010
So he told that "Today all those who are seeking the truth,

00:12:11.160 --> 00:12:14.180
seeking their Self-realization, Atma sakshatkara,

00:12:15.100 --> 00:12:18.110
those who are going into giri and kandharas,

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:21.240
into the mountains and in the valleys,

00:12:23.000 --> 00:12:25.160
searching God all over the world;

00:12:26.100 --> 00:12:27.240
these people will be born

00:12:28.050 --> 00:12:32.060
as ordinary householders during Kali Yuga.

00:12:33.080 --> 00:12:35.060
There will be bhram, no doubt,

00:12:35.130 --> 00:12:37.110
people will be in sabhram.

00:12:38.010 --> 00:12:41.120
Illusion will be there, and the confusion will be there

00:12:41.120 --> 00:12:43.100
- that I will create, no doubt -

00:12:43.210 --> 00:12:46.200
but because of this confusion only,

00:12:47.090 --> 00:12:52.020
these simple householders will seek the truth.

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:55.110
And that's why

00:12:55.230 --> 00:12:59.170
that is the time they will get their Atma sakshatkara."

00:13:00.240 --> 00:13:06.040
It's a - lots of prophecies have been there

00:13:06.150 --> 00:13:09.210
in our shastras about these times,

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:14.020
but specially

00:13:15.020 --> 00:13:19.080
Bhrigumuni in "Nadigranth" has described about these times.

00:13:19.220 --> 00:13:24.130
If you tally them with the timing of today,

00:13:24.130 --> 00:13:27.120
it is exactly this time.

00:13:28.220 --> 00:13:33.030
After the death of Raghwindra Swami this will happen,

00:13:33.150 --> 00:13:35.210
and that's what is happening now.

00:13:36.180 --> 00:13:39.090
For you people it is very important to understand that

00:13:39.170 --> 00:13:44.130
Raghwindra Swami was in this area and he did a lot of work,

00:13:44.230 --> 00:13:48.120
and now the time has come to complete his work;

00:13:50.070 --> 00:13:53.000
also Ramana Maharshi.

00:13:53.180 --> 00:13:55.070
They didn't know how to explain,

00:13:55.130 --> 00:13:57.190
so they took to maunavart.

00:13:58.080 --> 00:14:01.020
People like Gyaneshwara at the age of twenty-three,

00:14:01.100 --> 00:14:03.100
writing such wonderful things,

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:05.170
like "Amruta anubhavi ..." is a book,

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:09.080
I think the last word on spirituality.

00:14:10.080 --> 00:14:13.020
They had to get into samadhis at a such a young age of

00:14:13.090 --> 00:14:14.220
twenty-three years,

00:14:15.080 --> 00:14:18.090
because nobody tried to understand them.

00:14:18.170 --> 00:14:19.230
So much of ritualism,

00:14:20.060 --> 00:14:21.070
so much of conditioning,

00:14:21.140 --> 00:14:24.030
so much of reading that nobody wanted to know

00:14:24.100 --> 00:14:25.100
what they were talking.

00:14:25.180 --> 00:14:28.020
Everybody thought, "We know everything,"

00:14:28.120 --> 00:14:32.240
and that's how this kind of a satisfaction that they had.

00:14:34.110 --> 00:14:35.140
Kabira has said,

00:14:35.210 --> 00:14:38.060
Kaise samjhaun, sab jag andhaa -

00:14:38.160 --> 00:14:41.190
"How am I to explain, the whole world is blind."

00:14:42.120 --> 00:14:47.140
But this is what we have to achieve in our evolution,

00:14:47.230 --> 00:14:50.200
this is what we have to jump into.

00:14:51.070 --> 00:14:55.070
To become the spirit is told by all the scriptures -

00:14:55.240 --> 00:14:58.090
not only India, everywhere.

00:14:58.180 --> 00:15:01.020
If you take Tao, if you take Zen,

00:15:01.100 --> 00:15:07.240
if you go to the Jewish or to the Christian philosophies,

00:15:08.070 --> 00:15:10.220
or to the Islamic, everywhere it is said

00:15:11.070 --> 00:15:13.100
that you have to become your Self,

00:15:13.210 --> 00:15:15.190
you have to have self-knowledge.

00:15:16.080 --> 00:15:18.110
Of course, anybody said like that,

00:15:18.190 --> 00:15:22.140
those people who are in charge of religion

00:15:22.220 --> 00:15:25.050
or at the helm of affairs, making money

00:15:25.150 --> 00:15:27.200
or creating power out of it,

00:15:28.030 --> 00:15:30.200
people using religion for power or money;

00:15:31.070 --> 00:15:34.060
they didn't like it, so they said, "They are heretics.

00:15:34.170 --> 00:15:37.200
This is blasphemy. They have no special knowledge."

00:15:38.040 --> 00:15:40.180
And that's how they have been punishing people,

00:15:41.010 --> 00:15:43.180
troubling people, torturing them.

00:15:46.010 --> 00:15:49.000
But the time has come now for all the seekers

00:15:49.160 --> 00:15:54.180
to get their Self-realization, Atma sakshatkara.

00:15:55.120 --> 00:15:57.060
Yesterday I told you how it works out

00:15:57.120 --> 00:15:59.060
through kundalini awakening.

00:16:00.100 --> 00:16:02.020
About kundalini people have written

00:16:02.080 --> 00:16:04.220
all kinds of nonsensical things which is not true.

00:16:05.080 --> 00:16:07.070
I am your Mother, I'm going to tell you truth,

00:16:07.130 --> 00:16:10.000
I'm not going to tell you something false.

00:16:10.220 --> 00:16:13.080
Even if you don't like it let Me tell you,

00:16:13.190 --> 00:16:16.000
because this is for your benevolence,

00:16:16.090 --> 00:16:18.200
for your good, for your hita.

00:16:21.220 --> 00:16:24.230
So when the kundalini rises,

00:16:25.230 --> 00:16:28.010
she passes through your

00:16:28.080 --> 00:16:30.190
different centers which are subtle centers,

00:16:31.120 --> 00:16:32.220
and nourishes them,

00:16:33.030 --> 00:16:35.030
pierces through your fontanel bone area

00:16:35.090 --> 00:16:38.000
and connects you to the all-pervading Power,

00:16:38.060 --> 00:16:40.030
about which we do not know.

00:16:41.150 --> 00:16:45.070
Then from your hands you feel vibrations,

00:16:45.210 --> 00:16:47.240
which are called as Chaitanya lahari.

00:16:49.120 --> 00:16:53.050
Adi Shankaracharya has called it "Saundarya lahari,"

00:16:54.140 --> 00:16:57.080
because you can judge the saundarya with this.

00:16:59.160 --> 00:17:01.140
Beautifully he has described it.

00:17:01.230 --> 00:17:04.010
But how much they tortured him

00:17:06.060 --> 00:17:07.170
- think of it,

00:17:08.010 --> 00:17:10.070
person like Adi Shankaracharya - I mean,

00:17:11.030 --> 00:17:12.160
I don't know what to say.

00:17:13.020 --> 00:17:17.050
The one who gave such secrets about the Mother,

00:17:17.190 --> 00:17:20.090
such great descriptions;

00:17:21.120 --> 00:17:23.190
he was tortured for what?

00:17:24.080 --> 00:17:27.090
What wrong did he do that he should have been tortured?

00:17:29.210 --> 00:17:34.010
Now we have to stand up with the truth,

00:17:34.100 --> 00:17:37.120
and must say that "Mother, we have to have the truth,

00:17:37.180 --> 00:17:39.150
and truth and nothing else."

00:17:41.020 --> 00:17:44.160
I told you yesterday that Atma

00:17:45.160 --> 00:17:48.080
is the reflection of God Almighty in our heart.

00:17:48.190 --> 00:17:50.220
In these days of scientific

00:17:51.100 --> 00:17:55.140
conditioning this is a new type, apart from the "dharmic"

00:17:56.050 --> 00:17:59.210
scientific conditioning in which every scientist thinks

00:18:00.020 --> 00:18:01.000
that he knows everything.

00:18:01.060 --> 00:18:03.190
They don't know anything, take it from Me.

00:18:07.010 --> 00:18:08.130
It's absurd.

00:18:09.120 --> 00:18:11.010
Now you have seen so many scientists

00:18:11.090 --> 00:18:12.230
coming up and telling you about Sahaja Yoga.

00:18:13.090 --> 00:18:16.170
They have accepted because they have experimented.

00:18:17.150 --> 00:18:21.090
I told them that Mooladhara Chakra,

00:18:21.150 --> 00:18:23.120
the first chakra, Mooladhara,

00:18:24.070 --> 00:18:26.070
is made of carbon atoms,

00:18:26.130 --> 00:18:28.160
because it is made of Prithvi (means earth)... tattwa.

00:18:29.070 --> 00:18:33.220
And if you photograph the carbon atom

00:18:36.000 --> 00:18:39.060
and make a model out of it

00:18:40.010 --> 00:18:42.050
and then take a photograph, say, from left side,

00:18:42.130 --> 00:18:44.040
you'll see the right side,

00:18:44.100 --> 00:18:48.160
and you'll see actually "Aum" written down.

00:18:49.110 --> 00:18:51.160
If you see it from the right side,

00:18:51.220 --> 00:18:54.160
on the left side you will see a swastika.

00:18:55.030 --> 00:18:57.080
But if you see from down upward,

00:18:57.190 --> 00:18:59.150
you will see a cross.

00:19:00.190 --> 00:19:04.130
There is, really I must tell you a Dr. Worlikar

00:19:04.210 --> 00:19:05.240
who is a very famous doctor,

00:19:06.050 --> 00:19:12.050
he missed his prize in the Nobel Prize because,

00:19:12.130 --> 00:19:13.220
perhaps, he was an Indian.

00:19:14.120 --> 00:19:16.100
He's the one who experimented with three,

00:19:16.180 --> 00:19:21.030
four other Sahaja yogi scientists, and they said it is so.

00:19:24.020 --> 00:19:25.100
It is so.

00:19:26.000 --> 00:19:32.000
There is such a little knowledge with these scientists,

00:19:32.060 --> 00:19:35.220
because they are seeing things from outside.

00:19:36.150 --> 00:19:39.150
With Sahaja Yoga you go from inside.

00:19:40.140 --> 00:19:43.070
And everybody says the same thing,

00:19:45.070 --> 00:19:48.020
because - now you see Me standing here

00:19:48.090 --> 00:19:50.210
wearing a white sari and a red border;

00:19:51.040 --> 00:19:52.180
everybody knows, everybody feels.

00:19:53.020 --> 00:19:54.210
I don't have to tell you, you know it,

00:19:55.080 --> 00:19:57.210
you see it and you see this is so.

00:19:58.080 --> 00:19:59.240
But once you get your realization,

00:20:00.050 --> 00:20:02.110
whatever you feel on your hands

00:20:03.190 --> 00:20:06.190
is felt by everyone the same.

00:20:07.020 --> 00:20:10.110
Even if you take ten children and tie up their eyes,

00:20:10.200 --> 00:20:13.150
ask them, "What is this gentleman suffering from?" -

00:20:14.010 --> 00:20:15.210
they don't know if it's a lady or a gentleman,

00:20:16.040 --> 00:20:19.180
eyes are tied up - they'll put supposing one finger like this.

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:21.120
That means his Vishuddhi is bad.

00:20:21.200 --> 00:20:23.080
You ask the person, "Have you got throat trouble?" -

00:20:23.170 --> 00:20:25.120
"How do you know?"

00:20:26.090 --> 00:20:31.010
We know because this finger is Shri Krishna's finger,

00:20:31.150 --> 00:20:33.090
Shri Krishna's place,

00:20:33.240 --> 00:20:35.160
this is the throat.

00:20:36.150 --> 00:20:37.150
It all relates.

00:20:37.230 --> 00:20:42.180
Mythology is not all absurd.

00:20:43.100 --> 00:20:46.140
Ninety percent is absolutely what it was.

00:20:46.230 --> 00:20:49.170
Of course there are some absurd things that have walked in,

00:20:50.000 --> 00:20:53.010
but ninety percent mythology, so-called mythology

00:20:53.090 --> 00:20:55.070
is absolutely there.

00:20:56.160 --> 00:20:58.160
Now, we go to temples.

00:20:59.120 --> 00:21:02.070
We think, this is a temple, going is very good and all that.

00:21:02.130 --> 00:21:04.100
But we don't know what we are doing,

00:21:04.220 --> 00:21:07.100
what we are praying, whom are we praying,

00:21:07.160 --> 00:21:10.160
what are these deities, how they work in ourselves,

00:21:11.000 --> 00:21:16.030
where do they reside within ourselves, what is their job?

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:18.170
How to please them?

00:21:19.150 --> 00:21:20.130
We don't know anything;

00:21:20.210 --> 00:21:23.000
but you ask these foreigners, they know everything.

00:21:25.150 --> 00:21:28.060
First of all they got fed up with Christianity,

00:21:28.150 --> 00:21:30.030
that's one thing.

00:21:30.180 --> 00:21:34.010
They just got fed up with all the nonsense they found out,

00:21:34.070 --> 00:21:36.120
because they're very intelligent, you can see,

00:21:37.120 --> 00:21:39.070
and their conditioning was much less.

00:21:39.160 --> 00:21:40.200
And they started thinking,

00:21:41.020 --> 00:21:44.120
"After all, we don't know why they do like this."

00:21:48.080 --> 00:21:50.080
Then they were just ready.

00:21:50.180 --> 00:21:53.160
At that time we exported lots of fake gurus -

00:21:54.020 --> 00:21:56.080
the West export is the fake gurus.

00:21:56.170 --> 00:22:00.160
Thank God we are saved, we are poor - that's a blessing.

00:22:02.060 --> 00:22:04.240
So lots of fake gurus went there and made a lot of money,

00:22:05.060 --> 00:22:07.040
and here also we had lots of them.

00:22:07.100 --> 00:22:10.200
I mean, we are just good at it, creating lots of fake gurus.

00:22:11.180 --> 00:22:13.190
And they befooled people one after another,

00:22:14.020 --> 00:22:15.110
made a lot of money.

00:22:15.190 --> 00:22:17.160
It's all money-oriented.

00:22:20.000 --> 00:22:21.230
In the beginning it was so difficult for Me

00:22:22.060 --> 00:22:25.190
because they all used to come with big gusto to fight Me,

00:22:26.010 --> 00:22:28.150
because I said you can't take money in the name of God -

00:22:28.220 --> 00:22:30.140
that was too much.

00:22:31.060 --> 00:22:34.030
"How can She say that you cannot take money?"

00:22:34.240 --> 00:22:36.180
But now it's better.

00:22:37.090 --> 00:22:39.210
One by one all of them got nicely exposed,

00:22:40.020 --> 00:22:41.120
and more will be exposed.

00:22:41.200 --> 00:22:43.140
I don't have to tell you about them;

00:22:43.220 --> 00:22:45.090
they will be exposed, one by one.

00:22:45.200 --> 00:22:49.060
If there is light, all darkness has to go,

00:22:49.150 --> 00:22:53.090
and everything that is there has to be exposed.

00:22:54.130 --> 00:22:56.240
So everyone feels the same,

00:22:57.240 --> 00:22:59.210
there is no quarrel about it;

00:23:00.080 --> 00:23:05.100
because the spirit is the reflection of God Almighty,

00:23:06.140 --> 00:23:11.160
it's one God, who reflects Sadashiva.

00:23:12.200 --> 00:23:15.050
Sadashiva, who is a witness to the work of

00:23:15.110 --> 00:23:17.010
the Primordial Mother, Adi Shakti,

00:23:17.120 --> 00:23:19.050
is just witnessing the play,

00:23:19.140 --> 00:23:20.190
just witnessing.

00:23:21.010 --> 00:23:23.000
In you He is witnessing as Atma,

00:23:23.060 --> 00:23:26.120
but He doesn't come into your attention, He's there.

00:23:28.040 --> 00:23:32.130
And His attention

00:23:33.210 --> 00:23:39.050
is only limited because He has not to

00:23:39.150 --> 00:23:44.160
any way interfere with your freedom.

00:23:45.010 --> 00:23:47.130
So He keeps to Himself, He is just watching.

00:23:47.200 --> 00:23:48.160
That is the "auto."

00:23:48.240 --> 00:23:51.020
When we say "autonomous nervous system" that is the auto,

00:23:51.090 --> 00:23:52.120
that's the spirit.

00:23:52.180 --> 00:23:56.190
Now it's the reflection of one Sadashiva.

00:23:57.050 --> 00:24:00.070
Naturally all the reflections have to be the same,

00:24:00.210 --> 00:24:03.000
their effects have to be the same.

00:24:03.130 --> 00:24:07.130
Of course, before realization is the reflection on a stone,

00:24:07.200 --> 00:24:10.200
we can call it, or on a wall,

00:24:11.050 --> 00:24:14.050
or maybe on some sort of a opaque thing.

00:24:14.180 --> 00:24:20.100
After realization you become reflectors,

00:24:20.210 --> 00:24:23.210
beautiful reflectors, and it reflects you.

00:24:24.070 --> 00:24:26.140
And everyone reflects the same thing.

00:24:26.240 --> 00:24:29.190
So the effect of Atma sakshatkara

00:24:30.020 --> 00:24:31.220
is the same on every person,

00:24:32.050 --> 00:24:35.050
that first he starts feeling this cool breeze in his hands,

00:24:35.120 --> 00:24:38.090
then out of his fontanel bone area.

00:24:39.000 --> 00:24:40.220
All of them feel the same way.

00:24:41.040 --> 00:24:43.120
Then they start feeling these centers

00:24:43.200 --> 00:24:46.170
and finding out what's wrong.

00:24:47.100 --> 00:24:52.230
Also all of them become thoughtlessly aware,

00:24:53.100 --> 00:24:57.020
first stage which we call as nirvichara samadhi.

00:24:57.130 --> 00:24:59.120
Instantaneously it works.

00:24:59.190 --> 00:25:02.000
You may say, "Mother, it's very difficult.

00:25:02.080 --> 00:25:03.150
How does it happen?

00:25:03.220 --> 00:25:05.060
People had to go to Himalayas."

00:25:05.120 --> 00:25:08.030
All right, it doesn't matter, you don't have to go.

00:25:09.070 --> 00:25:14.190
Those days are gone. After all, the civilization,

00:25:15.100 --> 00:25:18.110
this tree of civilization has grown so big,

00:25:18.170 --> 00:25:20.090
its roots have to be grown;

00:25:20.190 --> 00:25:23.060
otherwise the whole civilization will be finished.

00:25:23.140 --> 00:25:26.000
And this is the knowledge of the roots,

00:25:26.090 --> 00:25:29.110
and that's why to know this knowledge you have to become

00:25:29.230 --> 00:25:31.200
subtler, sukshma.

00:25:32.200 --> 00:25:35.100
This is only possible when the kundalini rises

00:25:35.180 --> 00:25:37.170
and pierces through your fontanel bone,

00:25:37.240 --> 00:25:42.120
and makes you connected with the the all-pervading Power

00:25:42.240 --> 00:25:44.150
of God's love.

00:25:46.120 --> 00:25:48.210
So the first thing that you feel

00:25:49.050 --> 00:25:51.190
is collective consciousness,

00:25:52.110 --> 00:25:54.170
because everybody is the spirit.

00:25:55.100 --> 00:25:56.240
So you can feel another Atma,

00:25:57.060 --> 00:25:59.080
you can feel another Atma, you can feel another.

00:25:59.190 --> 00:26:01.200
You can feel their body, you can feel their mind,

00:26:02.030 --> 00:26:03.200
you can feel anything.

00:26:06.130 --> 00:26:09.000
This is the first quality you get,

00:26:09.110 --> 00:26:12.070
samuhik chetana, on your nervous system,

00:26:12.140 --> 00:26:15.080
on your central nervous system.

00:26:17.130 --> 00:26:20.050
Whatever you have got in your evolution

00:26:20.110 --> 00:26:23.240
is expressed on your central nervous system.

00:26:24.110 --> 00:26:25.200
Now see:

00:26:26.020 --> 00:26:28.090
for example, if you have a dog or a horse

00:26:28.170 --> 00:26:31.170
and you want to take him through a very dirty lane,

00:26:33.030 --> 00:26:34.160
it will go, it won't bother.

00:26:35.000 --> 00:26:37.110
But for a human being it is very difficult,

00:26:38.000 --> 00:26:40.170
because in our evolution our central nervous system

00:26:41.000 --> 00:26:45.060
has developed the sense of smell, a sense of beauty.

00:26:47.200 --> 00:26:48.180
All right.

00:26:49.070 --> 00:26:50.200
So this they have developed,

00:26:51.040 --> 00:26:52.150
and once they have developed,

00:26:52.210 --> 00:26:55.100
what happens that

00:26:56.090 --> 00:27:01.010
now we human beings are definitely higher than animals

00:27:01.240 --> 00:27:07.000
in our evolution, and in our subtler sensitivities.

00:27:07.200 --> 00:27:10.020
For a dog it doesn't matter what you put here,

00:27:10.100 --> 00:27:13.160
how you decorate, what color you wear, nothing;

00:27:14.070 --> 00:27:16.150
to us it is very important,

00:27:17.150 --> 00:27:21.020
because our sensitivity has improved.

00:27:21.160 --> 00:27:23.070
It has improved

00:27:24.020 --> 00:27:26.100
because of our evolutionary process,

00:27:26.190 --> 00:27:29.020
we have become human beings.

00:27:31.060 --> 00:27:35.000
But in the human stage we have one problem,

00:27:35.080 --> 00:27:40.070
and that problem is that we have developed two institutions

00:27:40.150 --> 00:27:44.040
in our head and it's called as ego and superego,

00:27:44.120 --> 00:27:48.010
and you call the ego and the conditioning.

00:27:49.130 --> 00:27:54.080
These two institutions on our head cross over and calcify,

00:27:54.180 --> 00:27:58.100
and we become a closed personality.

00:28:00.070 --> 00:28:02.050
When the kundalini rises,

00:28:02.130 --> 00:28:04.110
she passes through this Agnya Chakra

00:28:04.190 --> 00:28:08.140
which is on the optic chiasma, and sucks in these two,

00:28:09.000 --> 00:28:12.110
opens the Sahasrara, and the kundalini goes out.

00:28:13.190 --> 00:28:18.030
This is a living process, this is not that you can do.

00:28:18.110 --> 00:28:20.040
Supposing you want to sow a seed,

00:28:20.120 --> 00:28:22.180
you cannot pull out a primule, the Ankura

00:28:23.000 --> 00:28:24.140
and push it into the thing.

00:28:24.210 --> 00:28:29.200
You cannot make the seed sprout.

00:28:30.010 --> 00:28:32.210
It's a living process of a living God,

00:28:33.160 --> 00:28:35.120
and of a living energy.

00:28:35.180 --> 00:28:38.110
Please understand, there's a big difference.

00:28:40.230 --> 00:28:45.110
So this is working out spontaneously,

00:28:46.100 --> 00:28:49.070
the rising of the kundalini. She is your Mother,

00:28:49.160 --> 00:28:53.100
she moves very beautifully without troubling you.

00:28:53.170 --> 00:28:55.110
She knows her child very well.

00:28:55.210 --> 00:28:58.220
This is the chance she has to give realization to you.

00:28:59.050 --> 00:29:02.110
She has loved you all her life, all your lives,

00:29:02.200 --> 00:29:05.010
and she knows all about you, all your problems;

00:29:05.070 --> 00:29:07.040
like, a naughty boy you have been -

00:29:07.120 --> 00:29:08.190
"It doesn't matter," she says,

00:29:09.010 --> 00:29:10.210
"this is the chance to give them realization."

00:29:11.040 --> 00:29:13.240
It is she who comes up well, beautifully,

00:29:14.080 --> 00:29:17.100
works it out, pierces through.

00:29:18.000 --> 00:29:19.160
All this happens.

00:29:21.130 --> 00:29:24.070
But when she touches the Brahmarandra

00:29:24.150 --> 00:29:26.160
or pierces through the Brahmarandra,

00:29:27.150 --> 00:29:31.070
then the seat of Sadashiva is here.

00:29:31.170 --> 00:29:33.200
He has a reflection here, but the seat is here.

00:29:34.020 --> 00:29:36.220
These are the peethas in our head, seven peethas,

00:29:37.200 --> 00:29:40.060
and the chakras are down below.

00:29:41.090 --> 00:29:43.180
So when she pierces through that,

00:29:44.130 --> 00:29:47.160
what we do is actually we have touched

00:29:47.220 --> 00:29:48.210
the Feet of Sadashiva,

00:29:49.020 --> 00:29:51.020
and that's how in our heart the spirit

00:29:51.100 --> 00:29:53.130
enters into our attention.

00:29:54.220 --> 00:29:56.210
When the spirit enters into our attention

00:29:57.020 --> 00:29:59.100
we become enlightened, our attention is enlightened,

00:30:00.150 --> 00:30:03.010
and this attention

00:30:05.210 --> 00:30:11.040
is very alert and it knows everything.

00:30:12.080 --> 00:30:14.060
Sitting down here you can find out about people,

00:30:14.140 --> 00:30:16.140
what they are doing, on the chakras.

00:30:16.230 --> 00:30:19.030
You will not discuss what clothes they are wearing,

00:30:19.110 --> 00:30:20.230
how much money they have in the bank,

00:30:21.070 --> 00:30:23.170
but they will see where are they on their chakras,

00:30:23.230 --> 00:30:26.200
what's the problem is. Sitting here you can cure them,

00:30:27.120 --> 00:30:29.150
sitting here you can help them.

00:30:30.020 --> 00:30:32.140
But they have to be one with this all-pervading Power,

00:30:32.210 --> 00:30:34.050
that is important.

00:30:34.160 --> 00:30:37.130
If they are not, then it takes some time.

00:30:41.080 --> 00:30:46.160
So first of all you become nirvichar, nirvichar samadhi,

00:30:47.030 --> 00:30:49.170
and you start working out your collective consciousness

00:30:50.010 --> 00:30:51.170
by giving realizations to others.

00:30:52.000 --> 00:30:53.210
You become entitled to raise this kundalini,

00:30:54.030 --> 00:30:55.240
with your hands you can raise the kundalini.

00:30:56.090 --> 00:30:58.140
You know these people who are singing here,

00:30:58.240 --> 00:31:02.020
some of them have given realization to a thousand people,

00:31:03.040 --> 00:31:05.070
and you can do it also,

00:31:06.170 --> 00:31:08.100
because now you have the power.

00:31:08.170 --> 00:31:10.130
But the problem is,

00:31:11.230 --> 00:31:13.200
you have been given the throne,

00:31:14.070 --> 00:31:16.150
you have been made to sit on that,

00:31:17.020 --> 00:31:21.190
now you have been also adorned with a beautiful

00:31:22.040 --> 00:31:23.020
mukuta (means crown).

00:31:23.100 --> 00:31:24.220
But still you don't want to believe

00:31:25.050 --> 00:31:27.130
you have become the king, now how to make you believe?

00:31:28.150 --> 00:31:33.040
So the second point is self-confidence, is very difficult.

00:31:33.230 --> 00:31:39.150
They cannot believe that they have got Self-realization.

00:31:40.080 --> 00:31:42.220
And "Go ahead with it, work it out.

00:31:43.030 --> 00:31:45.140
You have become your own guru, go ahead with it"

00:31:45.220 --> 00:31:47.130
- they cannot, they are afraid.

00:31:47.210 --> 00:31:51.140
But all these horrible cheats, they have no realization,

00:31:51.210 --> 00:31:53.100
they have no knowledge, nothing.

00:31:53.190 --> 00:31:55.030
They become the dead gurus,

00:31:55.110 --> 00:31:57.050
have thousands of people behind them,

00:31:57.130 --> 00:32:00.160
make fool of them, make money and spoil their lives.

00:32:01.090 --> 00:32:04.000
While those who are Sahaja yogis,

00:32:04.090 --> 00:32:06.230
who have all the knowledge, everything:

00:32:07.180 --> 00:32:13.200
still they are so humble, they are so simple.

00:32:16.130 --> 00:32:18.200
But they know about everyone.

00:32:19.120 --> 00:32:21.050
Anyone who comes there, they know,

00:32:21.120 --> 00:32:23.060
"Ah, we know this one."

00:32:23.200 --> 00:32:26.030
They won't say it but they know, all of them.

00:32:26.090 --> 00:32:28.120
In their own

00:32:29.210 --> 00:32:34.130
science they will tell you "this is this" - they know.

00:32:35.020 --> 00:32:38.100
Then collectively they will work for that person.

00:32:38.230 --> 00:32:42.180
You will not know what they are doing,

00:32:43.160 --> 00:32:45.110
and it will work out.

00:32:49.170 --> 00:32:55.170
So the second nature of the spirit,

00:32:56.000 --> 00:32:58.230
apart from that it is a collective being,

00:32:59.070 --> 00:33:01.100
it is an absolute being.

00:33:01.190 --> 00:33:03.150
We live in a relative world -

00:33:04.180 --> 00:33:08.140
this is good, this is bad, that is this, this is that.

00:33:09.130 --> 00:33:12.060
But it's an absolute being, in the sense,

00:33:12.190 --> 00:33:16.080
you put your hands towards a photograph:

00:33:17.080 --> 00:33:20.170
immediately, if it is made by a realized soul,

00:33:20.230 --> 00:33:22.220
you'll start getting the vibrations.

00:33:23.110 --> 00:33:26.110
Think of anyone - was that a realized soul?

00:33:26.210 --> 00:33:28.070
Just put your hands.

00:33:28.150 --> 00:33:31.200
There are many if - people who don't believe in God,

00:33:32.010 --> 00:33:35.010
if He's God, so-called, don't believe in God.

00:33:35.080 --> 00:33:36.170
I mean, it's most unscientific,

00:33:37.000 --> 00:33:38.160
but supposing they don't believe in God,

00:33:39.000 --> 00:33:42.190
they have to just ask, "Mother, is there God?" - finished,

00:33:43.110 --> 00:33:45.170
they get the vibrations.

00:33:46.090 --> 00:33:49.210
All things can be proved.

00:33:50.040 --> 00:33:52.110
There is Pramaan (means proof) for everything,

00:33:52.180 --> 00:33:57.130
Pramaan for all that is said so far.

00:34:01.240 --> 00:34:05.050
This is a very great thing that happens to you,

00:34:05.160 --> 00:34:09.140
that you get the Pramaan out of your chaitanya.

00:34:11.120 --> 00:34:17.240
Then this chitta which is so attentive,

00:34:18.130 --> 00:34:21.220
which is so dynamic, which is so effective,

00:34:23.070 --> 00:34:25.100
also purifies you.

00:34:25.220 --> 00:34:27.220
It knows where is your problem,

00:34:28.030 --> 00:34:31.030
what chakra is catching, they tell you.

00:34:32.010 --> 00:34:36.200
Like I was there in Delhi,

00:34:37.160 --> 00:34:40.060
they brought three boys. "Mother, their Agnya is catching.

00:34:40.120 --> 00:34:42.140
Somehow or other we cannot clear it."

00:34:43.000 --> 00:34:45.060
That means they're egoistical.

00:34:45.170 --> 00:34:47.210
They also said, "Yes, Mother, we have Agnyas catching,

00:34:48.030 --> 00:34:49.050
we've got headaches."

00:34:49.130 --> 00:34:52.050
They're egoistical, but they didn't say they're egoistical.

00:34:52.140 --> 00:34:53.140
And they themselves are saying,

00:34:53.220 --> 00:34:56.140
"Yes, Mother, our Agnya's catching. Please clear it out."

00:34:57.030 --> 00:34:59.200
So you are yourself saying, "I am egoistical."

00:35:01.170 --> 00:35:04.220
Because that pains you now that that ego is paining you;

00:35:05.060 --> 00:35:08.000
so, "Mother, clear us out, we can't clear out this Agnya."

00:35:08.070 --> 00:35:10.230
"All right, come along, I'll clear it out."

00:35:12.120 --> 00:35:14.200
So you start judging yourself.

00:35:15.150 --> 00:35:18.040
You know about yourself what's wrong with you.

00:35:19.040 --> 00:35:20.190
"My this Nabhi is catching,

00:35:21.020 --> 00:35:24.040
my that chakra is catching, my that chakra is catching."

00:35:25.220 --> 00:35:27.140
They all know about themselves,

00:35:27.200 --> 00:35:30.090
and they know how to clarify and clear it out,

00:35:30.210 --> 00:35:34.010
and work it out. So you cleanse yourself.

00:35:34.180 --> 00:35:37.230
But the greatest cleansing comes when you are collective.

00:35:38.160 --> 00:35:41.180
Many people take My photograph,

00:35:42.050 --> 00:35:45.150
"Mother, we do puja, we sit down and meditate;

00:35:45.220 --> 00:35:49.030
but still again I got this trouble."

00:35:50.070 --> 00:35:52.030
You have to be in the collective,

00:35:52.110 --> 00:35:55.140
that is a very important part of Sahaja Yoga.

00:35:56.130 --> 00:35:59.230
Because now, you see, you don't have to go to Himalayas,

00:36:00.110 --> 00:36:03.090
not have to go and jump in the Ganges.

00:36:03.200 --> 00:36:06.010
You don't have to do any fasting,

00:36:06.240 --> 00:36:09.050
you don't have to say any Japaas (means chants), nothing.

00:36:09.130 --> 00:36:11.130
Only one thing: you be collective.

00:36:12.050 --> 00:36:16.130
Collective is the ocean of the attention of Almighty.

00:36:17.020 --> 00:36:19.160
Once you are in the collective you get cleansed.

00:36:19.240 --> 00:36:22.060
Like My finger, supposing - is all right,

00:36:22.140 --> 00:36:24.120
but supposing a nail is cut out and thrown,

00:36:24.200 --> 00:36:27.220
it won't grow. Nobody will pay attention to it.

00:36:28.060 --> 00:36:30.230
So you have to come to the collective.

00:36:32.030 --> 00:36:33.190
There, ego comes in.

00:36:34.050 --> 00:36:37.130
There are people who are very big, rich,

00:36:37.210 --> 00:36:39.100
very well-educated,

00:36:39.170 --> 00:36:43.190
or politicians - you know, big, big, big, big, big people.

00:36:44.150 --> 00:36:46.150
They find it difficult

00:36:47.070 --> 00:36:50.070
to come down to a humble place, is a center.

00:36:50.190 --> 00:36:53.080
They want another palace to be created for them,

00:36:53.160 --> 00:36:56.020
"otherwise how can we go there?"

00:36:57.110 --> 00:36:59.050
It's Mother's house.

00:36:59.220 --> 00:37:02.030
Even if your mother is humble,

00:37:02.190 --> 00:37:04.240
she doesn't have much money - "All right, doesn't matter,

00:37:05.070 --> 00:37:07.010
it's my mother's house."

00:37:07.120 --> 00:37:10.110
And they don't come, and then they lose vibrations.

00:37:10.180 --> 00:37:13.030
This is a very common failing, specially in India,

00:37:13.110 --> 00:37:14.090
not in the West

00:37:14.180 --> 00:37:18.130
because they know what precious thing they have achieved.

00:37:18.240 --> 00:37:22.070
We have no idea as to what it is that we have achieved,

00:37:22.130 --> 00:37:24.100
our Atma sakshatkara.

00:37:25.010 --> 00:37:28.020
So again next year I come,

00:37:28.120 --> 00:37:31.040
"Mother, I have this problem, that problem.

00:37:31.110 --> 00:37:34.020
I've been meditating at home all right."

00:37:34.100 --> 00:37:36.170
If you don't come to the collective,

00:37:37.020 --> 00:37:38.170
you cannot cleanse yourself.

00:37:38.240 --> 00:37:42.080
That's the only way in Sahaja Yoga you can cleanse yourself,

00:37:42.160 --> 00:37:45.160
and you can be above everything else.

00:37:48.000 --> 00:37:51.180
So when the kundalini passes through your Agnya Chakra,

00:37:52.180 --> 00:37:55.200
you become thoughtlessly aware.

00:37:57.010 --> 00:38:01.010
A thought rises and falls, another thought rises and falls.

00:38:01.240 --> 00:38:04.150
Some come from the past, some come from the future;

00:38:04.230 --> 00:38:06.210
but we are not in the present.

00:38:07.050 --> 00:38:09.190
If I say "you be in the present," you cannot be.

00:38:11.110 --> 00:38:15.050
That's why kundalini awakening is a happening

00:38:17.030 --> 00:38:19.140
which attracts your attention inside.

00:38:19.220 --> 00:38:22.220
Just like this sari of Mine is the kundalini coming up -

00:38:23.050 --> 00:38:24.120
see now it's spread out like that;

00:38:24.190 --> 00:38:26.000
but when she's coming up

00:38:26.060 --> 00:38:28.110
she's pulling all the attention inside.

00:38:30.090 --> 00:38:31.230
And that's how your attention goes in.

00:38:32.060 --> 00:38:34.180
And when she pierces through,

00:38:35.070 --> 00:38:37.060
then there is a space in between

00:38:37.130 --> 00:38:39.130
the thought called as "vilamba"

00:38:40.040 --> 00:38:42.150
- this, of course, so everybody knows perhaps -

00:38:43.020 --> 00:38:45.090
that increases, that is the present.

00:38:45.180 --> 00:38:47.120
So we have to be in the vartamaan (means present),

00:38:47.180 --> 00:38:48.210
we have to be in the present,

00:38:49.040 --> 00:38:51.100
then we are thoughtless.

00:38:52.160 --> 00:38:56.140
Say the waves of water rising, falling,

00:38:56.240 --> 00:38:59.160
you are facing the water;

00:39:02.020 --> 00:39:04.220
but when you are in the water you are afraid,

00:39:05.060 --> 00:39:06.030
frightened,

00:39:06.120 --> 00:39:08.050
when you have problems you are frightened.

00:39:08.120 --> 00:39:12.170
But supposing somebody takes you out and puts you into a

00:39:12.230 --> 00:39:15.030
boat, then you see it,

00:39:15.210 --> 00:39:17.130
you can solve your problems.

00:39:17.210 --> 00:39:19.180
But supposing you know how to swim,

00:39:19.240 --> 00:39:23.020
you can jump down and save many others.

00:39:23.100 --> 00:39:26.040
So in three stages you move.

00:39:29.210 --> 00:39:31.140
So the growth only takes place

00:39:31.220 --> 00:39:33.040
when you are thoughtlessly aware.

00:39:33.110 --> 00:39:35.140
And that can be achieved in collectivity

00:39:35.220 --> 00:39:38.190
as well as in your meditation,

00:39:39.160 --> 00:39:41.160
for which you don't have to pay.

00:39:42.020 --> 00:39:45.230
Some people have an opening introduction lecture free,

00:39:46.080 --> 00:39:48.230
and then the second one is banking.

00:39:51.120 --> 00:39:53.030
Sahaja Yoga is not like that.

00:39:53.090 --> 00:39:55.150
All this nonsense is not in Sahaja Yoga.

00:39:55.230 --> 00:39:59.090
It's reality, and reality cannot be purchased.

00:39:59.150 --> 00:40:01.050
Actually God doesn't know bank,

00:40:01.150 --> 00:40:03.120
He doesn't know money.

00:40:04.100 --> 00:40:06.140
He doesn't understand anything about money.

00:40:06.220 --> 00:40:10.080
He has not made money: this is your headache,not His.

00:40:12.090 --> 00:40:14.230
Of course, supposing I had to fly I have to pay,

00:40:15.060 --> 00:40:16.070
it is all right.

00:40:16.170 --> 00:40:18.170
If I have to get a hall I have to pay;

00:40:19.000 --> 00:40:21.120
but for the hall, not for God.

00:40:24.240 --> 00:40:26.180
For awakening,

00:40:27.100 --> 00:40:31.130
for enlightenment you cannot charge any fee.

00:40:32.040 --> 00:40:36.020
Even for darshan I am told people charge money - imagine.

00:40:38.170 --> 00:40:42.000
For them everything is money, money, money, money, money.

00:40:42.080 --> 00:40:45.170
How can they rise to the level of spirit?

00:40:48.010 --> 00:40:50.180
And we are so simple, you know,

00:40:51.060 --> 00:40:54.090
the bhaktas are so simple. "All right, you want five rupees,

00:40:54.180 --> 00:40:57.060
I'll sell my ring and give you.

00:40:57.170 --> 00:41:00.050
You want this, I'll give you this."

00:41:00.160 --> 00:41:03.100
There was a guru in America

00:41:04.080 --> 00:41:08.010
who had, I think, forty-eight Rolls Royce or something,

00:41:08.090 --> 00:41:10.000
I had forgotten the counts,

00:41:10.070 --> 00:41:12.170
and he wanted one more.

00:41:13.120 --> 00:41:15.180
So he told his disciples

00:41:16.060 --> 00:41:19.010
that "You should somehow or other get me one more

00:41:19.090 --> 00:41:21.180
Rolls Royce, then I'll come to England."

00:41:22.050 --> 00:41:24.160
So poor things were living on potatoes,

00:41:25.020 --> 00:41:26.130
starving themselves.

00:41:26.220 --> 00:41:29.040
So one of the Sahaja yogis said, "What are you doing?

00:41:29.120 --> 00:41:31.070
Why does he want a Rolls Royce?

00:41:31.170 --> 00:41:33.170
What is his interest in Rolls Royce?"

00:41:34.010 --> 00:41:36.230
He says, "You know, we are just giving him the metal,

00:41:37.060 --> 00:41:39.090
but he's giving us the spirit."

00:41:39.160 --> 00:41:40.160
Can you imagine it?

00:41:40.230 --> 00:41:42.190
Metal can be exchanged for spirit!

00:41:43.020 --> 00:41:45.020
Must be some sort of a bhoot badha

00:41:45.100 --> 00:41:46.160
he must be putting on them,

00:41:46.240 --> 00:41:48.220
and that in English language is "spirit."

00:41:49.070 --> 00:41:51.030
English language is very dangerous,

00:41:51.140 --> 00:41:58.160
because "spirit" is wine,

00:41:59.030 --> 00:42:02.230
"spirit" is Atma and "spirit" is a bhoot -

00:42:03.080 --> 00:42:05.180
I don't know which spirit they mean!

00:42:10.230 --> 00:42:12.160
So,

00:42:15.090 --> 00:42:19.190
the relationship

00:42:20.150 --> 00:42:24.090
with God if it has to establish,

00:42:24.180 --> 00:42:28.170
we have to become first of all the spirit;

00:42:29.180 --> 00:42:33.230
then only this relation can be established.

