you shouldn't use them everywhere.

00:55:17.090 --> 00:55:19.000
Now, this is a dangerous question! -

00:55:19.060 --> 00:55:21.200
Does non-vegetarian food affect the sadhana?

00:55:22.040 --> 00:55:24.060
Is vegetarian food is preferable?

00:55:24.130 --> 00:55:27.230
Now if I say anything you are going to be angry!

00:55:29.070 --> 00:55:30.190
But I'll tell you.

00:55:31.070 --> 00:55:37.020
In Sahaja Yoga, you are not supposed to eat any flesh of

00:55:37.100 --> 00:55:39.220
a bigger animal than yourself.

00:55:47.200 --> 00:55:49.220
If you are vegetarian, you could be vegetarian;

00:55:50.060 --> 00:55:52.050
if you are non-vegetarian you can be non-veg.

00:55:52.150 --> 00:55:55.180
But it depends on what sort of a personality you are.

00:55:56.090 --> 00:55:58.040
Supposing you are a right-sided person,

00:55:58.140 --> 00:56:00.170
you'd better be vegetarians.

00:56:00.240 --> 00:56:02.120
But if you are left-sided,

00:56:02.200 --> 00:56:04.100
it's better to take to proteins.

00:56:04.180 --> 00:56:06.210
So we're talking proteins and carbohydrates.

00:56:07.070 --> 00:56:08.150
Take any kind of proteins.

00:56:08.230 --> 00:56:12.100
Now we Indians don't eat any proteins.

00:56:15.130 --> 00:56:16.160
Except for Idli (a South indian dish)

00:56:16.240 --> 00:56:19.030
I don't think we eat any proteins.

00:56:19.140 --> 00:56:21.220
That too, we have rice with it.

00:56:23.050 --> 00:56:25.050
Proteins must be eaten by Indians,

00:56:25.130 --> 00:56:26.110
I am of that opinion,

00:56:26.190 --> 00:56:29.000
because we have become so weak.

00:56:30.060 --> 00:56:32.230
As it is, we are so frightened of income tax,

00:56:33.060 --> 00:56:35.030
this tax, tax;

00:56:35.200 --> 00:56:37.150
plus we are so weak,

00:56:37.230 --> 00:56:41.120
because we eat absolutely insipid food.

00:56:41.190 --> 00:56:43.190
So we should eat nourishing food,

00:56:44.020 --> 00:56:46.130
specially proteins in any form.

00:56:46.220 --> 00:56:50.000
But not the animal which is bigger than you.

00:56:51.140 --> 00:56:53.000
Like people eat horses -

00:56:53.080 --> 00:56:55.060
I don't know what else they'll be doing, anything;

00:56:55.140 --> 00:56:57.040
elephant, I think!

00:57:05.100 --> 00:57:08.180
For everyone there is no prescription.

00:57:09.150 --> 00:57:12.190
According to your nature you should eat.

00:57:13.220 --> 00:57:16.140
I mean, so many people don't do Sahaja Yoga when I say this,

00:57:16.220 --> 00:57:18.100
just imagine.

00:57:19.000 --> 00:57:21.100
They miss their Atma sakshatkara because of this.

00:57:21.160 --> 00:57:23.190
I mean, how did you become a vegetarian?

00:57:24.020 --> 00:57:25.240
Because your mother was a vegetarian,

00:57:26.190 --> 00:57:27.230
what else?

00:57:29.090 --> 00:57:31.040
From where did you learn vegetarianism?

00:57:31.120 --> 00:57:32.160
Supposing you were a Muslim,

00:57:32.240 --> 00:57:36.070
then you would have eaten somebody's heads also!

00:57:40.200 --> 00:57:44.190
So luckily you are born in a Hindu community,

00:57:45.020 --> 00:57:47.120
but we go too far with it.

00:57:48.010 --> 00:57:49.240
Morning till evening -

00:57:50.080 --> 00:57:54.000
I mean, this ritualism is so much in Madras also

00:57:54.080 --> 00:57:55.080
that they told Me,

00:57:55.140 --> 00:57:58.060
"Mother, Sahaja Yoga can never work in Madras."

00:57:58.140 --> 00:58:00.000
I said, "Why?"

00:58:00.090 --> 00:58:02.170
"Because people are not at all sahaj.

00:58:03.010 --> 00:58:05.010
In the morning they must get up at four o'clock,

00:58:05.070 --> 00:58:08.110
have their bath, go to the temple, come back.

00:58:08.210 --> 00:58:10.070
If one day they don't do it,

00:58:10.160 --> 00:58:13.130
then the whole day they are like mad people,

00:58:15.100 --> 00:58:17.130
thinking they have committed the greatest sin -

00:58:17.200 --> 00:58:19.170
this routine must be done."

00:58:20.030 --> 00:58:22.030
There is no routine in Sahaja Yoga.

00:58:22.130 --> 00:58:24.100
It's a living process.

00:58:25.130 --> 00:58:28.130
There is no routine in living process.

00:58:29.080 --> 00:58:32.030
Whenever the flower wants, it will flower.

00:58:34.060 --> 00:58:37.170
So why kill yourself with these rituals?

00:58:38.080 --> 00:58:40.190
This is our problem in the Hindu religion,

00:58:41.010 --> 00:58:42.060
the same with the Christians;

00:58:42.140 --> 00:58:44.220
I mean, everybody is competing.

00:58:47.040 --> 00:58:50.070
God has created this world for us to enjoy.

00:58:51.240 --> 00:58:52.200
I tell you,

00:58:53.010 --> 00:58:56.160
if you give up this you'll be very much absolutely relaxed.

00:58:57.040 --> 00:58:58.160
Forget it!

00:59:00.120 --> 00:59:02.130
At the most, five minutes in the morning

00:59:02.240 --> 00:59:04.020
Sahaja Yoga meditation,

00:59:04.080 --> 00:59:07.030
and ten minutes in the evening before sleeping - finished.

00:59:07.110 --> 00:59:08.190
For that we have a center,

00:59:09.030 --> 00:59:11.160
you go and see them - that's all.

00:59:13.060 --> 00:59:15.170
The rest God will do for you.

